:::Banzai-Tron:::

Banzai-Tron: Well, you see, ive died before. I once was a bot named 
Treadshot, but i was killed by this Maximal bitch in a battle at the CF. My 
partner Hurricane brought me back to base and was about to bury my body, but 
then the inventor, Wheeljack, said he could fix me. He fixed me up, and here 
i am. the names Banzai-Tron.  So anyway i obviusly swore revenge on this 
Airazor chick as soon as i was brought back.  I found her flying and slagged 
her easy.  But then her boyfriend or something goes ballistic. I challenge 
him to a man-to-man fight and i almost had him, but then he hit me with his 
flamehtrower. Next thing i know im here talking to you.  Im burned pretty 
bad, so get me to a CR as soon as possible.
